{"15.26":{"start":"15.26","dur":"2","text":"I&#39;m a savant,"},"17.26":{"start":"17.26","dur":"2","text":"or more precisely,"},"19.26":{"start":"19.26","dur":"2","text":"a high-functioning"},"21.26":{"start":"21.26","dur":"2","text":"autistic savant."},"23.26":{"start":"23.26","dur":"2","text":"It&#39;s a rare condition."},"25.26":{"start":"25.26","dur":"3","text":"And rarer still when accompanied,"},"28.26":{"start":"28.26","dur":"2","text":"as in my case,"},"30.26":{"start":"30.26","dur":"2","text":"by self-awareness"},"32.26":{"start":"32.26","dur":"3","text":"and a mastery of language."},"35.26":{"start":"35.26","dur":"3","text":"Very often when I meet someone"},"38.26":{"start":"38.26","dur":"2","text":"and they learn this about me,"},"40.26":{"start":"40.26","dur":"3","text":"there&#39;s a certain kind of awkwardness."},"43.26":{"start":"43.26","dur":"3","text":"I can see it in their eyes."},"46.26":{"start":"46.26","dur":"3","text":"They want to ask me something."},"49.26":{"start":"49.26","dur":"2","text":"And in the end, quite often,"},"51.26":{"start":"51.26","dur":"3","text":"the urge is stronger than they are"},"54.26":{"start":"54.26","dur":"2","text":"and they blurt it out:"},"56.26":{"start":"56.26","dur":"2","text":"&quot;If I give you my date of birth,"},"58.26":{"start":"58.26","dur":"2","text":"can you tell me what day of the week I was born on?&quot;"},"60.26":{"start":"60.26","dur":"3","text":"(Laughter)"},"63.26":{"start":"63.26","dur":"3","text":"Or they mention cube roots"},"66.26":{"start":"66.26","dur":"4","text":"or ask me to recite a long number or long text."},"70.26":{"start":"70.26","dur":"2","text":"I hope you&#39;ll forgive me"},"72.26":{"start":"72.26","dur":"3","text":"if I don&#39;t perform"},"75.26":{"start":"75.26","dur":"4","text":"a kind of one-man savant show for you today."},"79.26":{"start":"79.26","dur":"3","text":"I&#39;m going to talk instead"},"82.26":{"start":"82.26","dur":"2","text":"about something"},"84.26":{"start":"84.26","dur":"2","text":"far more interesting"},"86.26":{"start":"86.26","dur":"3","text":"than dates of birth or cube roots --"},"89.26":{"start":"89.26","dur":"2","text":"a little deeper"},"91.26":{"start":"91.26","dur":"3","text":"and a lot closer, to my mind, than work."},"94.26":{"start":"94.26","dur":"2","text":"I want to talk to you briefly"},"96.26":{"start":"96.26","dur":"3","text":"about perception."},"99.26":{"start":"99.26","dur":"3","text":"When he was writing the plays and the short stories"},"102.26":{"start":"102.26","dur":"2","text":"that would make his name,"},"104.26":{"start":"104.26","dur":"3","text":"Anton Chekhov kept a notebook"},"107.26":{"start":"107.26","dur":"2","text":"in which he noted down"},"109.26":{"start":"109.26","dur":"2","text":"his observations"},"111.26":{"start":"111.26","dur":"2","text":"of the world around him --"},"113.26":{"start":"113.26","dur":"2","text":"little details"},"115.26":{"start":"115.26","dur":"3","text":"that other people seem to miss."},"118.26":{"start":"118.26","dur":"3","text":"Every time I read Chekhov"},"121.26":{"start":"121.26","dur":"4","text":"and his unique vision of human life,"},"125.26":{"start":"125.26","dur":"2","text":"I&#39;m reminded of why I too"},"127.26":{"start":"127.26","dur":"2","text":"became a writer."},"129.26":{"start":"129.26","dur":"2","text":"In my books,"},"131.26":{"start":"131.26","dur":"2","text":"I explore the nature of perception"},"133.26":{"start":"133.26","dur":"3","text":"and how different kinds of perceiving"},"136.26":{"start":"136.26","dur":"2","text":"create different kinds of knowing"},"138.26":{"start":"138.26","dur":"3","text":"and understanding."},"143.26":{"start":"143.26","dur":"2","text":"Here are three questions"},"145.26":{"start":"145.26","dur":"2","text":"drawn from my work."},"147.26":{"start":"147.26","dur":"2","text":"Rather than try to figure them out,"},"149.26":{"start":"149.26","dur":"3","text":"I&#39;m going to ask you to consider for a moment"},"152.26":{"start":"152.26","dur":"2","text":"the intuitions"},"154.26":{"start":"154.26","dur":"2","text":"and the gut instincts"},"156.26":{"start":"156.26","dur":"2","text":"that are going through your head and your heart"},"158.26":{"start":"158.26","dur":"3","text":"as you look at them."},"161.26":{"start":"161.26","dur":"3","text":"For example, the calculation:"},"164.26":{"start":"164.26","dur":"2","text":"can you feel where on the number line"},"166.26":{"start":"166.26","dur":"3","text":"the solution is likely to fall?"},"169.26":{"start":"169.26","dur":"3","text":"Or look at the foreign word and the sounds:"},"172.26":{"start":"172.26","dur":"2","text":"can you get a sense of the range of meanings"},"174.26":{"start":"174.26","dur":"3","text":"that it&#39;s pointing you towards?"},"177.26":{"start":"177.26","dur":"3","text":"And in terms of the line of poetry,"},"180.26":{"start":"180.26","dur":"2","text":"why does the poet use the word hare"},"182.26":{"start":"182.26","dur":"3","text":"rather than rabbit?"},"186.26":{"start":"186.26","dur":"2","text":"I&#39;m asking you to do this"},"188.26":{"start":"188.26","dur":"4","text":"because I believe our personal perceptions, you see,"},"192.26":{"start":"192.26","dur":"2","text":"are at the heart"},"194.26":{"start":"194.26","dur":"2","text":"of how we acquire knowledge."},"196.26":{"start":"196.26","dur":"2","text":"Aesthetic judgments,"},"198.26":{"start":"198.26","dur":"3","text":"rather than abstract reasoning,"},"201.26":{"start":"201.26","dur":"2","text":"guide and shape the process"},"203.26":{"start":"203.26","dur":"3","text":"by which we all come to know"},"206.26":{"start":"206.26","dur":"2","text":"what we know."},"208.26":{"start":"208.26","dur":"3","text":"I&#39;m an extreme example of this."},"211.26":{"start":"211.26","dur":"3","text":"My worlds of words and numbers"},"214.26":{"start":"214.26","dur":"2","text":"blur with color, emotion"},"216.26":{"start":"216.26","dur":"2","text":"and personality."},"218.26":{"start":"218.26","dur":"2","text":"As Juan said,"},"220.26":{"start":"220.26","dur":"3","text":"it&#39;s the condition that scientists call synesthesia,"},"223.26":{"start":"223.26","dur":"2","text":"an unusual cross-talk"},"225.26":{"start":"225.26","dur":"3","text":"between the senses."},"231.26":{"start":"231.26","dur":"2","text":"Here are the numbers one to 12"},"233.26":{"start":"233.26","dur":"2","text":"as I see them --"},"235.26":{"start":"235.26","dur":"4","text":"every number with its own shape and character."},"239.26":{"start":"239.26","dur":"2","text":"One is a flash of white light."},"241.26":{"start":"241.26","dur":"5","text":"Six is a tiny and very sad black hole."},"246.26":{"start":"246.26","dur":"3","text":"The sketches are in black and white here,"},"249.26":{"start":"249.26","dur":"2","text":"but in my mind they have colors."},"251.26":{"start":"251.26","dur":"2","text":"Three is green."},"253.26":{"start":"253.26","dur":"2","text":"Four is blue."},"255.26":{"start":"255.26","dur":"3","text":"Five is yellow."},"260.26":{"start":"260.26","dur":"2","text":"I paint as well."},"262.26":{"start":"262.26","dur":"3","text":"And here is one of my paintings."},"265.26":{"start":"265.26","dur":"4","text":"It&#39;s a multiplication of two prime numbers."},"269.26":{"start":"269.26","dur":"2","text":"Three-dimensional shapes"},"271.26":{"start":"271.26","dur":"3","text":"and the space they create in the middle"},"274.26":{"start":"274.26","dur":"2","text":"creates a new shape,"},"276.26":{"start":"276.26","dur":"3","text":"the answer to the sum."},"279.26":{"start":"279.26","dur":"2","text":"What about bigger numbers?"},"281.26":{"start":"281.26","dur":"4","text":"Well you can&#39;t get much bigger than Pi,"},"285.26":{"start":"285.26","dur":"2","text":"the mathematical constant."},"287.26":{"start":"287.26","dur":"2","text":"It&#39;s an infinite number --"},"289.26":{"start":"289.26","dur":"2","text":"literally goes on forever."},"291.26":{"start":"291.26","dur":"2","text":"In this painting that I made"},"293.26":{"start":"293.26","dur":"4","text":"of the first 20 decimals of Pi,"},"297.26":{"start":"297.26","dur":"2","text":"I take the colors"},"299.26":{"start":"299.26","dur":"3","text":"and the emotions and the textures"},"302.26":{"start":"302.26","dur":"2","text":"and I pull them all together"},"304.26":{"start":"304.26","dur":"5","text":"into a kind of rolling numerical landscape."},"309.26":{"start":"309.26","dur":"3","text":"But it&#39;s not only numbers that I see in colors."},"312.26":{"start":"312.26","dur":"2","text":"Words too, for me,"},"314.26":{"start":"314.26","dur":"2","text":"have colors and emotions"},"316.26":{"start":"316.26","dur":"2","text":"and textures."},"318.26":{"start":"318.26","dur":"2","text":"And this is an opening phrase"},"320.26":{"start":"320.26","dur":"2","text":"from the novel &quot;Lolita.&quot;"},"322.26":{"start":"322.26","dur":"4","text":"And Nabokov was himself synesthetic."},"326.26":{"start":"326.26","dur":"2","text":"And you can see here"},"328.26":{"start":"328.26","dur":"3","text":"how my perception of the sound L"},"331.26":{"start":"331.26","dur":"2","text":"helps the alliteration"},"333.26":{"start":"333.26","dur":"3","text":"to jump right out."},"336.26":{"start":"336.26","dur":"2","text":"Another example:"},"338.26":{"start":"338.26","dur":"2","text":"a little bit more mathematical."},"340.26":{"start":"340.26","dur":"2","text":"And I wonder if some of you will notice"},"342.26":{"start":"342.26","dur":"2","text":"the construction of the sentence"},"344.26":{"start":"344.26","dur":"3","text":"from &quot;The Great Gatsby.&quot;"},"348.26":{"start":"348.26","dur":"3","text":"There is a procession of syllables --"},"351.26":{"start":"351.26","dur":"2","text":"wheat, one;"},"353.26":{"start":"353.26","dur":"2","text":"prairies, two;"},"355.26":{"start":"355.26","dur":"3","text":"lost Swede towns, three --"},"358.26":{"start":"358.26","dur":"2","text":"one, two, three."},"360.26":{"start":"360.26","dur":"4","text":"And this effect is very pleasant on the mind,"},"364.26":{"start":"364.26","dur":"2","text":"and it helps the sentence"},"366.26":{"start":"366.26","dur":"3","text":"to feel right."},"369.26":{"start":"369.26","dur":"2","text":"Let&#39;s go back to the questions"},"371.26":{"start":"371.26","dur":"3","text":"I posed you a moment ago."},"374.26":{"start":"374.26","dur":"3","text":"64 multiplied by 75."},"377.26":{"start":"377.26","dur":"3","text":"If some of you play chess,"},"380.26":{"start":"380.26","dur":"2","text":"you&#39;ll know that 64"},"382.26":{"start":"382.26","dur":"3","text":"is a square number,"},"385.26":{"start":"385.26","dur":"2","text":"and that&#39;s why chessboards,"},"387.26":{"start":"387.26","dur":"2","text":"eight by eight,"},"389.26":{"start":"389.26","dur":"3","text":"have 64 squares."},"392.26":{"start":"392.26","dur":"2","text":"So that gives us a form"},"394.26":{"start":"394.26","dur":"3","text":"that we can picture, that we can perceive."},"397.26":{"start":"397.26","dur":"3","text":"What about 75?"},"400.26":{"start":"400.26","dur":"2","text":"Well if 100,"},"402.26":{"start":"402.26","dur":"3","text":"if we think of 100 as being like a square,"},"405.26":{"start":"405.26","dur":"3","text":"75 would look like this."},"408.26":{"start":"408.26","dur":"2","text":"So what we need to do now"},"410.26":{"start":"410.26","dur":"2","text":"is put those two pictures"},"412.26":{"start":"412.26","dur":"2","text":"together in our mind --"},"414.26":{"start":"414.26","dur":"3","text":"something like this."},"417.26":{"start":"417.26","dur":"4","text":"64 becomes 6,400."},"421.26":{"start":"421.26","dur":"4","text":"And in the right-hand corner,"},"425.26":{"start":"425.26","dur":"2","text":"you don&#39;t have to calculate anything."},"427.26":{"start":"427.26","dur":"2","text":"Four across, four up and down --"},"429.26":{"start":"429.26","dur":"3","text":"it&#39;s 16."},"432.26":{"start":"432.26","dur":"2","text":"So what the sum is actually asking you to do"},"434.26":{"start":"434.26","dur":"2","text":"is 16,"},"436.26":{"start":"436.26","dur":"3","text":"16, 16."},"439.26":{"start":"439.26","dur":"2","text":"That&#39;s a lot easier"},"441.26":{"start":"441.26","dur":"3","text":"than the way that the school taught you to do math, I&#39;m sure."},"444.26":{"start":"444.26","dur":"2","text":"It&#39;s 16, 16, 16, 48,"},"446.26":{"start":"446.26","dur":"2","text":"4,800 --"},"448.26":{"start":"448.26","dur":"2","text":"4,800,"},"450.26":{"start":"450.26","dur":"3","text":"the answer to the sum."},"453.26":{"start":"453.26","dur":"2","text":"Easy when you know how."},"455.26":{"start":"455.26","dur":"3","text":"(Laughter)"},"458.26":{"start":"458.26","dur":"3","text":"The second question was an Icelandic word."},"461.26":{"start":"461.26","dur":"3","text":"I&#39;m assuming there are not many people here"},"464.26":{"start":"464.26","dur":"2","text":"who speak Icelandic."},"466.26":{"start":"466.26","dur":"3","text":"So let me narrow the choices down to two."},"471.26":{"start":"471.26","dur":"2","text":"Hnugginn:"},"473.26":{"start":"473.26","dur":"2","text":"is it a happy word,"},"475.26":{"start":"475.26","dur":"2","text":"or a sad word?"},"477.26":{"start":"477.26","dur":"2","text":"What do you say?"},"480.26":{"start":"480.26","dur":"2","text":"Okay."},"482.26":{"start":"482.26","dur":"2","text":"Some people say it&#39;s happy."},"484.26":{"start":"484.26","dur":"2","text":"Most people, a majority of people,"},"486.26":{"start":"486.26","dur":"2","text":"say sad."},"488.26":{"start":"488.26","dur":"4","text":"And it actually means sad."},"492.26":{"start":"492.26","dur":"3","text":"(Laughter)"},"495.26":{"start":"495.26","dur":"3","text":"Why do, statistically,"},"498.26":{"start":"498.26","dur":"2","text":"a majority of people"},"500.26":{"start":"500.26","dur":"2","text":"say that a word is sad, in this case,"},"502.26":{"start":"502.26","dur":"3","text":"heavy in other cases?"},"505.26":{"start":"505.26","dur":"3","text":"In my theory, language evolves in such a way"},"508.26":{"start":"508.26","dur":"2","text":"that sounds match,"},"510.26":{"start":"510.26","dur":"3","text":"correspond with, the subjective,"},"513.26":{"start":"513.26","dur":"2","text":"with the personal,"},"515.26":{"start":"515.26","dur":"2","text":"intuitive experience"},"517.26":{"start":"517.26","dur":"2","text":"of the listener."},"520.26":{"start":"520.26","dur":"3","text":"Let&#39;s have a look at the third question."},"524.26":{"start":"524.26","dur":"3","text":"It&#39;s a line from a poem by John Keats."},"527.26":{"start":"527.26","dur":"3","text":"Words, like numbers,"},"530.26":{"start":"530.26","dur":"3","text":"express fundamental relationships"},"533.26":{"start":"533.26","dur":"2","text":"between objects"},"535.26":{"start":"535.26","dur":"2","text":"and events and forces"},"537.26":{"start":"537.26","dur":"2","text":"that constitute our world."},"539.26":{"start":"539.26","dur":"3","text":"It stands to reason that we, existing in this world,"},"542.26":{"start":"542.26","dur":"2","text":"should in the course of our lives"},"544.26":{"start":"544.26","dur":"3","text":"absorb intuitively those relationships."},"547.26":{"start":"547.26","dur":"3","text":"And poets, like other artists,"},"550.26":{"start":"550.26","dur":"3","text":"play with those intuitive understandings."},"553.26":{"start":"553.26","dur":"3","text":"In the case of hare,"},"556.26":{"start":"556.26","dur":"2","text":"it&#39;s an ambiguous sound in English."},"558.26":{"start":"558.26","dur":"3","text":"It can also mean the fibers that grow from a head."},"561.26":{"start":"561.26","dur":"2","text":"And if we think of that --"},"563.26":{"start":"563.26","dur":"2","text":"let me put the picture up --"},"565.26":{"start":"565.26","dur":"3","text":"the fibers represent vulnerability."},"569.26":{"start":"569.26","dur":"3","text":"They yield to the slightest movement"},"572.26":{"start":"572.26","dur":"3","text":"or motion or emotion."},"575.26":{"start":"575.26","dur":"4","text":"So what you have is an atmosphere"},"579.26":{"start":"579.26","dur":"2","text":"of vulnerability and tension."},"581.26":{"start":"581.26","dur":"2","text":"The hare itself, the animal --"},"583.26":{"start":"583.26","dur":"3","text":"not a cat, not a dog, a hare --"},"586.26":{"start":"586.26","dur":"2","text":"why a hare?"},"588.26":{"start":"588.26","dur":"2","text":"Because think of the picture --"},"590.26":{"start":"590.26","dur":"2","text":"not the word, the picture."},"592.26":{"start":"592.26","dur":"2","text":"The overlong ears,"},"594.26":{"start":"594.26","dur":"2","text":"the overlarge feet,"},"596.26":{"start":"596.26","dur":"3","text":"helps us to picture, to feel intuitively,"},"599.26":{"start":"599.26","dur":"3","text":"what it means to limp"},"602.26":{"start":"602.26","dur":"3","text":"and to tremble."},"605.26":{"start":"605.26","dur":"2","text":"So in these few minutes,"},"607.26":{"start":"607.26","dur":"2","text":"I hope I&#39;ve been able to share"},"609.26":{"start":"609.26","dur":"3","text":"a little bit of my vision of things"},"612.26":{"start":"612.26","dur":"3","text":"and to show you"},"615.26":{"start":"615.26","dur":"3","text":"that words can have colors and emotions,"},"618.26":{"start":"618.26","dur":"3","text":"numbers, shapes and personalities."},"621.26":{"start":"621.26","dur":"2","text":"The world is richer,"},"623.26":{"start":"623.26","dur":"2","text":"vaster"},"625.26":{"start":"625.26","dur":"3","text":"than it too often seems to be."},"628.26":{"start":"628.26","dur":"3","text":"I hope that I&#39;ve given you the desire"},"631.26":{"start":"631.26","dur":"3","text":"to learn to see the world with new eyes."},"634.26":{"start":"634.26","dur":"2","text":"Thank you."},"636.26":{"start":"636.26","dur":"11","text":"(Applause)"}}